Para resolver o erro "42P07: a relação 'profiles' já existe", é necessário utilizar a cláusula `IF NOT EXISTS` no seu script SQL. Além disso, notei que na sua imagem os comandos SQL parecem estar traduzidos para o português (ex: `CRIAR POLÍTICA` em vez de `CREATE POLICY`). O editor do Supabase (PostgreSQL) aceita apenas comandos em **Inglês**.

Abaixo, apresento o script SQL corrigido e a integração completa dos módulos restantes.

### 1. Schema SQL Corrigido (Inglês + Resiliente)
Execute este bloco no **SQL Editor** do seu Supabase. Ele cria as tabelas apenas se elas não existirem e configura as políticas de segurança.

```sql
-- 1. Tabela de Perfis (Associação)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS profiles (
  id uuid REFERENCES auth.users ON DELETE CASCADE PRIMARY KEY,
  association_name text DEFAULT 'Associação Integrada',
  cnpj text DEFAULT '00.000.000/0001-00',
  updated_at timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now()
);

-- 2. Tabela de Contas
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS accounts (
  id uuid DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id uuid REFERENCES auth.users ON DELETE CASCADE NOT NULL,
  name text NOT NULL,
  type text CHECK (type IN ('bank', 'cash', 'savings')),
  initial_balance numeric DEFAULT 0,
  description text,
  created_at timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now()
);

-- 3. Tabela de Categorias
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS categories (
  id uuid DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id uuid REFERENCES auth.users ON DELETE CASCADE NOT NULL,
  name text NOT NULL,
  type text CHECK (type IN ('income', 'expense'))
);

-- 4. Tabela de Transações
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS transactions (
  id uuid DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id uuid REFERENCES auth.users ON DELETE CASCADE NOT NULL,
  date date NOT NULL,
  description text NOT NULL,
  amount numeric NOT NULL,
  type text CHECK (type IN ('income', 'expense')),
  category text,
  account_id uuid REFERENCES accounts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  status text CHECK (status IN ('pending', 'completed', 'cancelled')),
  payment_method text,
  notes text,
  attachment text,
  reconciled boolean DEFAULT false,
  created_at timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now()
);

-- 5. Tabela de Documentos
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS documents (
  id uuid DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id uuid REFERENCES auth.users ON DELETE CASCADE NOT NULL,
  name text NOT NULL,
  file_url text,
  folder text,
  created_at timestamp with time zone DEFAULT now()
);

-- Habilitar RLS (Row Level Security)
ALTER TABLE profiles ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE accounts ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE categories ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE transactions ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE documents ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

-- Políticas de Acesso (Evita erro se já existirem usando DO block ou DROP primeiro)
DO $$ 
BEGIN
    DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can manage their own profile" ON profiles;
    CREATE POLICY "Users can manage their own profile" ON profiles FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = id);

    DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can manage their own accounts" ON accounts;
    CREATE POLICY "Users can manage their own accounts" ON accounts FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);

    DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can manage their own categories" ON categories;
    CREATE POLICY "Users can manage their own categories" ON categories FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);

    DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can manage their own transactions" ON transactions;
    CREATE POLICY "Users can manage their own transactions" ON transactions FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);

    DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can manage their own documents" ON documents;
    CREATE POLICY "Users can manage their own documents" ON documents FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);
END $$;
```

### 2. Atualizações no Código

Vou ajustar o `FinanceContext` para mapear corretamente os campos do banco de dados (snake_case) para o TypeScript (camelCase) e garantir que todos os módulos funcionem.

